ANS(fun_cmp("-1+abs(x+2)", vars=>["x"]));

TEXT(EV3(<<'EOT'));
$BR Hint: 
Ask what happens to the vertex of the graph of \(f(x) = |x|\)
EOT

SOLUTION(EV3(<<'EOT'));
$BR $BBOLD Solution:$EBOLD
The vertex of the modified function is at \((-2,-1)\).
To move it there we replace \(f(x) = |x|\) with
\(g(x) = |x+2| -1.\)
EOT



